ea81311367e4343aeaa542763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F153907_63e62acea81311367e4343aeaa542763.jpg&h=2f2b9e77&s={SIZE}\" />left leg"},{"pid":"0fac1c0bbcf1a8ad3020e5a4d42b4bd39833e869","tid":470208,"uid":60531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/154059_9eef1173251a0752aac91a5d3029f63e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F154059_9eef1173251a0752aac91a5d3029f63e.jpg&h=99324512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左右腳對比圖<br />\n見到有血管腫脈<br />\n呢個咩stage🙈<br />\n有無去到要做手術咁嚴重？"},{"pid":"9dc20f0e7ffd4b548632b93b18f0a158c38dabfc","tid":470208,"uid":121712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/154059_9eef1173251a0752aac91a5d3029f63e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F154059_9eef1173251a0752aac91a5d3029f63e.jpg&h=99324512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左右腳對比圖<br />\n見到有血管腫脈<br />\n呢個咩stage🙈<br />\n有無去到要做手術咁嚴重？</blockquote><br />\n睇落大約stage 2 3，有冇腳腫？"},{"pid":"abb791972a896ddedacd9accd5702fc5170343c5","tid":470208,"uid":68753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"就咁睇右腳C1 左腳C2<br />\n多數都係試左conservative treatment睇response先，好少一黎就手術<br />\n當然重有其他考慮，例如symptoms，disability，cosmetic concern，有無skin change / ulcer，compliance to stocking，contraindications to stocking e.g. PVD，underlying (uncommon) causes e.g. DVT, drug-related, malignancy<br />\n一個完整既history應該問埋<br />\n不過要注意stocking只係for symptoms control，只有打藥／手術先係definitive<br />\n如果真係想做手術就要做埋超聲波睇有無saphenous reflux<br />\n<br />\n壓力襪最好去配，因為呢家係for treatment，唔係prophylaxis，要graded compression<br />\n政府專科可以先睇普通門診再轉介，等幾耐就每個區都唔同（係睇地區架）"},{"pid":"9d80373740574176fcaac4f9045fd1c808bd4ac3","tid":470208,"uid":60531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/154059_9eef1173251a0752aac91a5d3029f63e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F154059_9eef1173251a0752aac91a5d3029f63e.jpg&h=99324512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左右腳對比圖<br />\n見到有血管腫脈<br />\n呢個咩stage🙈<br />\n有無去到要做手術咁嚴重？</blockquote><br />\n睇落大約stage 2 3，有冇腳腫？</blockquote><br />\n左腳腫過右腳， 按落去都有輕微水腫"},{"pid":"7a110177063dc768f1f3b7a4b8c318e741b28612","tid":470208,"uid":60531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇右腳C1 左腳C2<br />\n多數都係試左conservative treatment睇response先，好少一黎就手術<br />\n當然重有其他考慮，例如symptoms，disability，cosmetic concern，有無skin change / ulcer，compliance to stocking，contraindications to stocking e.g. PVD，underlying (uncommon) causes e.g. DVT, drug-related, malignancy<br />\n一個完整既history應該問埋<br />\n不過要注意stocking只係for symptoms control，只有打藥／手術先係definitive<br />\n如果真係想做手術就要做埋超聲波睇有無saphenous reflux<br />\n<br />\n壓力襪最好去配，因為呢家係for treatment，唔係prophylaxis，要graded compression<br />\n政府專科可以先睇普通門診再轉介，等幾耐就每個區都唔同（係睇地區架）</blockquote><br />\n叫左啊媽下次放假就去睇門診🙈"},{"pid":"c2e9a1266b6c728fc1a8017553d60145a6d53d86","tid":470208,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就咁睇右腳C1 左腳C2<br />\n多數都係試左conservative treatment睇response先，好少一黎就手術<br />\n當然重有其他考慮，例如symptoms，disability，cosmetic concern，有無skin change / ulcer，compliance to stocking，contraindications to stocking e.g. PVD，underlying (uncommon) causes e.g. DVT, drug-related, malignancy<br />\n一個完整既history應該問埋<br />\n不過要注意stocking只係for symptoms control，只有打藥／手術先係definitive<br />\n如果真係想做手術就要做埋超聲波睇有無saphenous reflux<br />\n<br />\n壓力襪最好去配，因為呢家係for treatment，唔係prophylaxis，要graded compression<br />\n政府專科可以先睇普通門診再轉介，等幾耐就每個區都唔同（係睇地區架）</blockquote><br />\n叫左啊媽下次放假就去睇門診🙈</blockquote><br />\n記住門診要早啲用電話捕住咁book"},{"pid":"b9e4fc33dadc99efa7be4e729a1e055d09a94e11","tid":470208,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:03:14.000Z","msg":"有冇買保險？"},{"pid":"04a5590ed108b8ff870cc9d84974b99e33e2c3c9","tid":470208,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:05:37.000Z","msg":"如果冇事第一時間買有關醫療 住院之類保險<br />\n我唔知會唔會翻發啦<br />\n但大吉利是之後出事又做手術可能有關腳嘅病都唔受保"}]}